My RF linking hasn't gotten past the pencil/paper stage yet,
but here is another option:
http://www.dvp.com/

Most all of my sonar efforts so far have been directed toward
software solutions for filtering out unwanted cross-talk.  The
next step will be to add one (or three) transducers to the
single 6500 board.

